<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Choose the category you’re interested in and make some bets.</span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-193543" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/image_20251009155324.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="655" /></p>
